<p><strong>Stack economics note:</strong> ActiveCampaign adds value only when custom/consultation volume justifies CRM — else Sequenzy + Klaviyo suffices for catalog-only demi-fine. Model operator hours alongside SaaS fees — governance debt shows up as discount margin leakage before it shows up as tool cost.</p>
