<p><strong>Stack economics note:</strong> Return rate on wrong-size rings tracked by email segment — education-heavy browse paths should show lower return rate than discount-first paths within 90 days. Model operator hours alongside SaaS fees — governance debt shows up as discount margin leakage before it shows up as tool cost.</p>
    </article>
    <div class="space-y-8">
      {toolReviews.map((review) => (
        <ToolReview app={appBySlug(review.slug)!} rank={review.rank} paragraphs={review.paragraphs} />
      ))}
    </div>
    <FaqSection faqs={faqs} title={`FAQ: ${segmentName}`} />
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
